short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copy all tabs URLs at once.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is an extension that allows a user to copy all tabs urls at once. Working in a project that requires resources and copy paste a lot of urls can be exhausting. Do it smart with that extension.
